<h2>Privacy Policy</h2>

<p>
    This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect the personal information you provide through the Customer Feedback Portal.
</p>

<h4>1. Information We Collect</h4>
<p>
    When you submit feedback through our portal, we collect your name, email address, rating, message, and the date/time of submission.
</p>

<h4>2. How We Use Your Information</h4>
<p>
    The information you provide is used solely for the purpose of:
</p>
<ul>
    <li>Reviewing and managing customer feedback</li>
    <li>Improving our services based on your suggestions</li>
    <li>Responding to concerns if necessary</li>
</ul>

<h4>3. Data Protection</h4>
<p>
    We take appropriate measures to secure your personal information and prevent unauthorized access, disclosure, or modification.
</p>

<h4>4. Sharing of Information</h4>
<p>
    Your data will not be sold or shared with third parties. It will only be accessed by authorized personnel for the purpose of managing feedback.
</p>

<h4>5. Your Rights</h4>
<p>
    You have the right to:
</p>
<ul>
    <li>Request a copy of your feedback data</li>
    <li>Request correction or deletion of your data</li>
    <li>Withdraw your consent at any time</li>
</ul>
<p>
    To exercise these rights, please contact us via the information provided below.
</p>

<h4>6. Contact Us</h4>
<p>
    If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, you can contact us at:
    <br /><strong>Email:</strong> support@customerportal.com
</p>

<h4>7. Changes to This Policy</h4>
<p>
